column4: "dougmck@pipeline.com.au Done after listening (again) to Keith Jarrett's 'Live in Tokyo' CD. After the rubato first chorus I tried to get the group improvisation kind of feel with bass and drums supporting the piano improvisation.\012"
"Chromatically descending chords on each melody note"
"Bass and drums in - start is close to the original melody"
"Non chord tones on beat resolve up 1/2 step to chord tones. (appoggiatura)"
"Block Chords approached from a step above. "
